item.title: DanTDM
item.description: DanTDM is funny, clever, and great. DanTDM is the best. His real name is Daniel, he is 28 years old. He got the gold YouTube button for getting the most likes on YouTube. DanTDM is a Dad and was born in Aldershot. His videos are entertaining because he plays all the games I enjoy. He has blue hair. When I grow up I want to be a great YouTuber like DanTDM.
